  "keyFeatures": [
    "Questionnaire-based risk profiling with automated portfolio recommendations",
    "Multi-step investment onboarding wizard for clients",
    "Admin approval workflows for funding, withdrawal, and portfolio strategy requests",
    "FNZ/Tapico trading integration with order execution and holdings tracking",
    "Keycloak SSO with PKCE authorization code flow",
    "Role-based access control with hierarchical permission scoping (global > company > branch > own)",
    "Automated user synchronization from SUS8 Redshift datalake (cron: 2 AM daily)",
    "Clean Architecture + CQRS backend pattern across NestJS services",
    "Schema ownership model — ms-robo-admin is sole database schema owner",
    "Dual-portal architecture: separate admin and client UIs with isolated JWT storage"
  ],
